name: Moody Blues Bracelet
description:
Cool winter blue Picasso and Czech beads with all sorts of interesting copper beads come together to make this wonderful bracelet and earring set.

Rich blue beads strung with warm and unique copper beads will put a smile on your face every-time you put it on your wrist and friends will be wondering where you got such a great winter bracelet!

This bracelet is a bit over 7.5 inches long with a interesting copper toggle clasp and a pair of matching earrings which hang 1.5 inches from the top of the copper lever back wires.

Cold weather never looked so good!

This set was part of the Indie Artisans Deep Winter Collection.
http://www.indieartisans.com/

name: Monet's Garden - Lampwork and Sterling Charm Bracelet
description:
A beautiful charm bracelet in fresh pastel lampwork, sterling and Czech beads coming together to make a very gorgeous bracelet that reminds you of Monet's garden.

A base bracelet of lampwork flower beads with a sterling silver toggle clasp then tucked between each bead lots of unique pastel beads from flowers to butterfly's!

A wonderful charm bracelet for your Spring and Summer delight!

Bracelet is a bit over 7.5 inches

Toggle clasp,beads and spacers are sterling silver

Rings are silver plate for strength and to keep there shine!

name: Tuscany Field - Turquoise and Keshi Pearl Necklace
description:
A unique necklace designed with turquoise nuggets and beads with copper pink colored keshi pearls.

Beautiful blue green turquoise nuggets strung with copper pink colored free formed keshi pearls make for a fun and different color and material combination that looks new and so up to date!

The necklace is 18 inches long with a copper toggle clasp and a great pair of matching earrings to make this a set that you will love to wear often!

Earrings are 1.5 inches long from the top of the copper ear wire.
